Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://techtimejourney.net/
Description: lightweight tabbed file manager for Linux
 Spin FM is a compact Qt file manager with tabbed navigation, configurable
 themes, drag and drop, freedesktop Trash support, removable USB storage
 controls, and an embedded audio player. Long-running file and device operations
 run outside the UI thread, while multimedia support is initialized on demand.
